  Match to continue  Jyoti tied 30th   Vilamoura: Jyoti Randhawa turned in an even-par 72 in the final round to sign off tied 30th at the Portugal Masters.   Chopra 15th   Las Vegas: Daniel Chopra carded four-under 68 in the final round to end tied 15th in the Justin Timberlake Shriners Hospitals for Children Open.   Somdev loses  New Delhi: Somdev Dev Varman and Nathan Healy went down 6-1, 3-6, 11-13 in the final of the $50,000 Calabasas Challenger event in California.
                                                                                                                                                               
